name: 7GODS
highlight: Create your destiny and wealth in the realm of Annrion! MetaMMORPG DeFi Game. Play, compete and earn!
summary: Take part in PvP and PvE Combat events, Explore the world around you and go on a number of fantastic quests, collect valuable items, interact with NPCs, slay the monsters, pet them in order to make them your companions in battles against the enemies.
